This is the README file for /math/u1/ftp/pub/sontag

The directory contains selected papers by Eduardo Sontag
-as well as temporary files intended for anonymous FTP retrieval.

The file

		papers.html

has titles, abstracts, publication data, and filenames.
(To see a filename: if there is a reference for instance to
   href="http://www.math.rutgers.edu/~sontag/FTP_DIR/foo.ps.gz"
then you want to retrieve the file foo.ps.gz)

*********************************************************

Most files are (gzip-)compressed postscript files
           (extension .ps.z or .ps.gz).
They should be retrieved by FTP only after setting file type to
           binary (BIN).
After retrieval, the command "gunzip (filename)" will decompress;
then the file can be printed in a postscript-capable printer.

Files ending .tex are tex, latex, or amstex files.
Files with extension .txt are plain text.

*********************************************************
